704	    <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" data-tip="Fraction of your account risked per trade. 0.01 = 1%. Lower is safer. Safe range: 0.005-0.02">Risk Per Trade</label><input class="form-input" id="set_risk_per_trade" type="number" step="0.001"></div>
705	    <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" data-tip="How far away the stop-loss is placed, as a multiple of ATR (average price range). Higher = wider stop, more room but more risk. Safe range: 1.5-3.0">Stop Loss ATR Mult</label><input class="form-input" id="set_stop_loss_atr_mult" type="number" step="0.1"></div>
