708	    <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" data-tip="Maximum allowed loss in a single day as a fraction of your account. 0.03 = 3%. Trading halts if exceeded. Safe range: 0.02-0.05">Daily Loss Limit</label><input class="form-input" id="set_daily_loss_limit" type="number" step="0.01"></div>
709	    <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" data-tip="Maximum allowed peak-to-trough decline. 0.10 = 10%. Trading halts if exceeded. This is your emergency brake. Safe range: 0.05-0.15">Max Drawdown</label><input class="form-input" id="set_max_drawdown" type="number" step="0.01"></div>
